content:
local TweenService = game:GetService("TweenService")
local TeleportService = game:GetService("TeleportService")
local TpPart = Vector3.new(40.63526916503906, 4.328062057495117, -27.253986358642578)
local placeId = 7957302362

if game.PlaceId ~= placeId then
    wait(10)
    TeleportService:Teleport(PLACE_ID)
else
    wait(3)
    local twInfo = TweenInfo.new(5,Enum.EasingStyle.Linear,Enum.EasingDirection.Out)

    local plr = game:GetService("Players").LocalPlayer
    local char = plr.Character

    TweenService:Create(char.HumanoidRootPart, twInfo, {Position = TpPart}):Play()
end
